Inputting codes into the keypad successfully will open [[Special:MyLanguage/portals portals]] to other VRChat worlds.
===Statue Island===
[[File:Sketchu Spring Statue Island.webp|thumb|none|Chess board that can be interacted with.]]A secluded plateau far south of spawn, the main feature being a chessboard with large interactable statues that act as chess pieces. The green music orb can be found here propped up on an elevated set of rocks. North of the area can be found a bridge that leads to one of several mirages in the world, a giant golem statue.
===Mindaro's Shrine===
[[File:Sketchu Spring Mindaro.webp|thumb|none|The empty shrine.]]
[[File:Sketchu Spring Mural.webp|thumb|251x251px|The Mural]]
Found in the dark sandstorms east of spawn. The area consists solely of the shrine, a small set of ruins with several pedestals corresponding to each one of Mindaro's Charms. The charms must be placed atop each pedestal corresponding to the symbol, in which it will begin to glow.